da'i</a> (1986)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Avraham_Sharir" title="Avraham Sharir">Sharir</a> (1986-88)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Dan_Meridor" title="Dan Meridor">Meridor</a> (1988-92)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/David_Libai" title="David Libai">Libai</a> (1992-96)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Ya%27akov_Ne%27eman" title="Ya'akov Ne'eman">Ne'eman</a> (1996)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Benjamin_Netanyahu" title="Benjamin Netanyahu">Netanyahu</a> (1996)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Tzachi_Hanegbi" title="Tzachi Hanegbi">Hanegbi</a> (1996-99)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Yossi_Beilin" title="Yossi Beilin">Beilin</a> (1999-2001)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Meir_Sheetrit" title="Meir Sheetrit">Sheetrit</a> (2001-2003)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Tommy_Lapid" title="Tommy Lapid">Lapid</a> (2003-04)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Tzipi_Livni" title="Tzipi Livni">Livni</a> (2004-06)*&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Haim_Ramon" title="Haim Ramon">Ramon</a> (2006)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Meir_Sheetrit" title="Meir Sheetrit">Sheetrit</a> (2006)*&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Ehud_Olmert" title="Ehud Olmert">Olmert</a> (2006)*&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Tzipi_Livni" title="Tzipi Livni">Livni</a> (2006-07)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Daniel_Friedmann" title="Daniel Friedmann">Friedmann</a> (2007-09)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Ya%27akov_Ne%2